{"tid":1964053,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩慘得過隔離坐左個勁撚污糟嘅同事？","createTime":"2020-04-08T14:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T08:28:36.000Z","uid":214261,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6c82b3807e45df7b6c2b8d0db916f7ea49f199fc","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近俾隔離個邋遢同事惹左流感，<br />\n都幾撚肯定係佢惹，佢未病好就返工，<br />\n（心諗：屌你咁搏做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔係有得升職加薪，間公司你有份咩）<br />\n<br />\n未有武肺之前已經成間房啲同事都戴口罩，<br />\n個個叫佢戴都唔撚戴，<br />\n話好焗同箍住隻耳，好辛苦<br />\n新年後再返工，公司貼左memo佢先戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬，有邊個唔辛苦咖？<br />\n<br />\n平時佢坐我隔離唔夠一米，<br />\n開會果時佢坐我對面飲水果時咳又無揞住<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁嘅時勢好心就注意下個人衛生啦，<br />\n平時你幾污糟我唔理呀，<br />\n但你咁樣係將快樂建築係我痛苦身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要病完抵抗力又差又辛苦<br />\n屌乸星，睇完醫生，claim醫保仲要貼多兩舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢平時掂完垃圾桶係唔撚會洗手、<br />\n然後又掂自己個口罩，又捽眼、<br />\n有時會除鞋，但佢對襪又踩返對鞋踩過嘅位、<br />\n飲野食野又就咁拉個口罩落下巴。<br />\n<br />\n出黎做野發覺要屌人好難，<br />\n神通廣大嘅連登仔可唔可以教毒撚點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（佢連senior同事都夠膽屌返轉頭）<br />\n<br />\n唔好答我：左右兩個同事都係勁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40de64c546c23abd26d1f4d03fc898ee80cbae4b","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63d294930c2efed3451a4d610fa32399b1bc8076","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"平時佢飲完啲水就咁擺過夜第二日又再飲<br />\n好撚難頂呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a541eeacf1647eead0219f1f4fb1e33a8ed7b6","tid":1964053,"uid":44854,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"我前後兩個同事都係勁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565466d0b40e04d675f11a0c2952d205041b4408","tid":1964053,"uid":14653,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"左右兩個同事都係勁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb391636665c4cad76e2f1ca298a333f5f36b27","tid":1964053,"uid":35456,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b05ed9cadc7d4adbd209265810c8eb549fb39dcf","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"565466d0b40e04d675f11a0c2952d205041b4408","tid":1964053,"uid":14653,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"左右兩個同事都係勁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一打唔洗找"},{"pid":"f55081740be8661c759c7a0abc130f76dc9b20e5","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efb391636665c4cad76e2f1ca298a333f5f36b27","tid":1964053,"uid":35456,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人唔好咁多性幻想"},{"pid":"09182b5a2977ef3d3bcc9eed6a8b410117a19909","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acd99537620825a25af4a66f28a200cd5d4e7237","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3969acc93ec8d63e221e5ff68b7435de6a20225","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07de0839c62beb0bd571d9846494f9f4271c0f31","tid":1964053,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{